cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper is about using deep reinforcement learning to control a dexterous multi-fingered hand for complex manipulation tasks. The focus is on robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), specifically deep reinforcement learning (DRL). The paper also mentions the use of natural policy gradients (cs.LG) and the tasks involve object recognition and manipulation (cs.CV) as well as door opening (cs.SY).
